name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. John Joseph KOEHLER, Jr., Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. John Joseph KOEHLER, Jr., Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM
AND NOW, this 2nd day of November, 2016, the matter is remanded to the Court of Common Pleas of Bradford County for disposition of Petitioner’s PCRA petition. See 42 Pa.C.S. § 9545(a) (“Original jurisdiction over a proceeding under this subchapter shall be in the court of common pleas.”).
opinions.author: PER CURIAM
